title: OS X 10.9 Pre-release Toolkit (Seed Config Utility, 10.9.2 13C32
description:
--------OS X 10.9 Mavericks Pre-release Toolkit--------

INCLUDES: Mavericks Seed Configuration Utility, OS X 10.9.2 Pre-Release Seed (13C32). All files are zipped for your convenience when downloading so you don't need as many seeders!

**Use this software at your own risk**



Mavericks Seed Configuration Utility:
    The Mavericks Seed Configuration Utility allows users with it installed to view pre-release OS X Mavericks updates and seeds on Software Update in the App Store. To install, run the Install Mavericks Seed Configuration Utility and complete the installer. After that, you will see pre-release seeds in the App Store. This is what registered mac developers use.

OS X 10.9.2 13C32:
    Included in this is the first developer seed for OS X 10.9.2, which is Build 13C32. This is if you don't want to use the seed configuration utility and instead just want the update. This IS the combo version. I'll post new versions of builds when they release, along with other OS X Software.


How to use:

1. Dezip
2. Open "Mavericks Seed Configuration Utility" or "OS X 10.9.2 Combo Update (13C32).pkg" depending on what you want.
3. Enjoy and please help by seeding!


      Expect more OS X software from me. Not just other builds of OS X Mavericks.
